{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012SfFemS4SMLRvJ8xodGA4a","type":"tool_result","content":"200\t\n201\t### FR-5: SOL/USD Price Display\n202\t\n203\tTransaction amounts are stored in lamports. The frontend displays them in SOL\n204\twith a USD estimate using the Pyth SOL/USD price feed (Hermes REST API —\n205\talready used for Close Call BTC/USD prices).\n206\t\n207\t- Backend exposes a cached `GET /price/sol-usd` endpoint (or piggybacks on an\n208\t  existing price infrastructure). Cache TTL ~60s.\n209\t- Frontend fetches the SOL/USD price and displays amounts as e.g.\n210\t  `0.50 SOL (~$75.00)`.\n211\t- If price is unavailable, show SOL amount only (no USD estimate). No error\n212\t  state — graceful degradation.\n213\t\n214\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n215\t- [x] Backend serves cached SOL/USD price from Pyth Hermes <!-- satisfied: routes/price.ts:10-66 — HermesClient, SOL/USD feed, 60s TTL cache, stale-on-error -->\n216\t- [x] Frontend displays lamport amounts as SOL with USD estimate <!-- satisfied: ProfileTransactions.tsx:14-24 formatSol(amount, solPrice) → \"0.50 SOL (~$75.00)\" -->\n217\t- [x] Graceful fallback to SOL-only when price unavailable <!-- satisfied: useSolPrice.ts returns null on error; formatSol omits USD when price=null -->\n218\t\n219\t---\n220\t\n221\t### FR-6: Player Profile Record\n222\t\n223\tA `player_profiles` table that stores the player's identity. Created automatically\n224\ton first wallet auth (JWT challenge-response) or waitlist signup. The wallet is\n225\tstored internally but **never exposed in API responses** — all public-facing\n226\treferences use `user_id` or `username`.\n227\t\n228\t**Schema:**\n229\t\n230\t| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |\n231\t|--------|------|-------------|-------|\n232\t| `id` | `BIGSERIAL` | PK | Internal DB key (not exposed) |\n233\t| `user_id` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Short random string, e.g. `usr_a8f3k2`. Public-facing identifier for API calls |\n234\t| `wallet` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Player wallet address. **Never exposed in public API responses** |\n235\t| `username` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Auto-generated on creation. Editable (freeform, 30-day cooldown) |\n236\t| `username_updated_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | | Null until first manual edit. Cooldown enforced from this timestamp |\n237\t| `avatar_url` | `TEXT` | | Null = use deterministic identicon derived from wallet. Explicit URL for future unlock/upload |\n238\t| `heat_multiplier` | `NUMERIC` | DEFAULT 1.0 | Reserved slot — always 1.0 until HEAT feature ships |\n239\t| `points_balance` | `BIGINT` | DEFAULT 0 | Reserved slot — always 0 until Points feature ships |\n240\t| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | NOT NULL DEFAULT now() | Profile creation time |\n241\t\n242\t**Indexes:**\n243\t- `uq_player_profiles_user_id` on `(user_id)` — public lookup\n244\t- `uq_player_profiles_wallet` on `(wallet)` — internal lookup / auth join\n245\t- `uq_player_profiles_username` on `(username)` — username lookup\n246\t\n247\t**User ID format:** `usr_` prefix + 8 random alphanumeric characters (lowercase).\n248\tGenerated once at profile creation, immutable.\n249\t\n250\t**Username auto-generation:** `{adjective}-{noun}-{4digits}`. On collision, retry\n251\twith new random suffix (max 5 retries, then fall back to `user-{random8}`).\n252\t\n253\t**Username edit rules:**\n254\t- Freeform: 3-20 characters, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`, no spaces\n255\t- Unique (case-insensitive)\n256\t- Editable once per 30 days (enforced via `username_updated_at`)\n257\t- First manual edit is free (cooldown starts from that edit, not from creation)\n258\t\n259\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n260\t- [ ] Migration `013_player_profiles.sql` creates table + indexes\n261\t- [ ] Profile auto-created on first JWT auth (challenge-response verify endpoint)\n262\t- [ ] Profile auto-created on waitlist signup (if applicable entry point exists)\n263\t- [ ] `user_id` is a short random string (`usr_` + 8 alphanumeric), immutable after creation\n264\t- [ ] Username auto-generated as `{adjective}-{noun}-{4digits}`, collision-safe\n265\t- [ ] Wallet address never appears in any public API response\n266\t- [ ] `heat_multiplier` and `points_balance` are reserved columns, default values only\n267\t\n268\t### FR-7: Username Management API\n269\t\n270\tPlayers can view and change their username.\n271\t\n272\t**Endpoints:**\n273\t\n274\t`PUT /profile/username`\n275\t- Auth: JWT required\n276\t- Body: `{ \"username\": \"my-new-name\" }`\n277\t- Validates: 3-20 chars, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`, unique (case-insensitive), 30-day cooldown\n278\t- Returns: `{ \"username\": \"my-new-name\", \"nextEditAvailableAt\": \"2026-05-01T...\" }`\n279\t- Errors: 400 (invalid format), 409 (taken), 429 (cooldown not expired)\n280\t\n281\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n282\t- [ ] Username change validates format (3-20 chars, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`)\n283\t- [ ] Username uniqueness enforced case-insensitively\n284\t- [ ] 30-day cooldown enforced from `username_updated_at`; first edit is free\n285\t- [ ] Successful edit updates both `username` and `username_updated_at`\n286\t- [ ] Returns next available edit timestamp in response\n287\t\n288\t### FR-8: Aggregate Player Stats API\n289\t\n290\tComputed stats from the existing `transactions` table. Served as part of the\n291\tprofile response (own profile) or public lookup (limited subset).\n292\t\n293\t**Own profile stats (authenticated):**\n294\t\n295\t| Stat | Computation |\n296\t|------|-------------|\n297\t| `gamesPlayed` | COUNT(DISTINCT match_id) where tx_type = 'deposit' |\n298\t| `totalWagered` | SUM(amount_lamports) where tx_type = 'deposit' |\n299\t| `totalWins` | COUNT(*) where tx_type = 'payout' |\n300\t| `winRate` | totalWins / gamesPlayed (0 if no games) |\n301\t| `winStreakCurrent` | Consecutive most-recent wins (across all games) |\n302\t| `winStreakBest` | Longest-ever consecutive win streak |\n303\t| `netPnl` | SUM(payout + refund) - SUM(deposit) |\n304\t| `gameBreakdown` | Per-game version of above (keyed by game name) |\n305\t\n306\t**Public stats (visible to others via lookup):**\n307\t\n308\t| Stat | Included |\n309\t|------|----------|\n310\t| `gamesPlayed` | Yes |\n311\t| `totalWins` | Yes |\n312\t| `winRate` | Yes |\n313\t| `totalWagered` | **No** |\n314\t| `netPnl` | **No** |\n315\t| `winStreakCurrent` | **No** |\n316\t| `winStreakBest` | **No** |\n317\t| `gameBreakdown` | **No** |\n318\t\n319\t**Win streak logic:** Ordered by `created_at DESC`, across all games. A `payout`\n320\trow = win. A `deposit` row with no corresponding `payout` for the same `match_id`\n321\t= loss. Refunds don't break or extend streaks. Streak resets on first loss\n322\twalking backward from most recent game.\n323\t\n324\t**Performance note:** Stats can be computed on-the-fly for now (single query per\n325\trequest). If latency becomes a problem, add a `player_stats_cache` materialized\n326\tview or summary table later — but don't pre-optimize.\n327\t\n328\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n329\t- [ ] `gamesPlayed`, `totalWagered`, `totalWins`, `winRate` computed correctly from `transactions`\n330\t- [ ] `winStreakCurrent` counts consecutive most-recent wins across all games\n331\t- [ ] `winStreakBest` tracks the longest-ever streak\n332\t- [ ] `netPnl` = total inflows (payout + refund) minus total outflows (deposit)\n333\t- [ ] `gameBreakdown` returns per-game stats keyed by frontend game name\n334\t- [ ] Public stats expose only `gamesPlayed`, `totalWins`, `winRate`\n335\t\n336\t### FR-9: Profile API Endpoints\n337\t\n338\tAll profile interaction points for the frontend.\n339\t\n340\t**Endpoints:**\n341\t\n342\t`GET /profile/me` (authenticated)\n343\t- Returns: full own profile + full stats\n344\t- Response shape:\n345\t  ```json\n346\t  {\n347\t    \"userId\": \"usr_a8f3k2\",\n348\t    \"username\": \"fierce-dragon-4821\",\n349\t    \"avatarUrl\": null,\n350\t    \"heatMultiplier\": 1.0,\n351\t    \"pointsBalance\": \"0\",\n352\t    \"stats\": {\n353\t      \"gamesPlayed\": 42,\n354\t      \"totalWagered\": \"150000000000\",\n355\t      \"totalWins\": 23,\n356\t      \"winRate\": 0.5476,\n357\t      \"winStreakCurrent\": 3,\n358\t      \"winStreakBest\": 7,\n359\t      \"netPnl\": \"5000000000\",\n360\t      \"gameBreakdown\": {\n361\t        \"coinflip\": { \"gamesPlayed\": 20, \"totalWins\": 11, \"winRate\": 0.55, \"totalWagered\": \"...\", \"netPnl\": \"...\" },\n362\t        \"lord-of-rngs\": { ... },\n363\t        \"close-call\": { ... }\n364\t      }\n365\t    },\n366\t    \"usernameNextEditAt\": \"2026-05-01T00:00:00Z\",\n367\t    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-15T10:00:00Z\"\n368\t  }\n369\t  ```\n370\t- `avatarUrl` null means frontend should render identicon from `userId`\n371\t- `totalWagered`, `netPnl`, `pointsBalance` as strings (BigInt safety)\n372\t\n373\t`GET /public-profile/:identifier` (public, no auth)\n374\t- Mounted at `/public-profile` (separate from `/profile/*` to avoid JWT middleware)\n375\t- `:identifier` resolves to either `user_id` (starts with `usr_`) or `username`\n376\t- Returns: public profile (no wallet, no tx history, limited stats)\n377\t- Response shape:\n378\t  ```json\n379\t  {\n380\t    \"userId\": \"usr_a8f3k2\",\n381\t    \"username\": \"fierce-dragon-4821\",\n382\t    \"avatarUrl\": null,\n383\t    \"heatMultiplier\": 1.0,\n384\t    \"stats\": {\n385\t      \"gamesPlayed\": 42,\n386\t      \"totalWins\": 23,\n387\t      \"winRate\": 0.5476\n388\t    },\n389\t    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-15T10:00:00Z\"\n390\t  }\n391\t  ```\n392\t- 404 if identifier not found\n393\t\n394\t**Acceptance Criteria:**\n395\t- [ ] `GET /profile/me` requires JWT, returns full profile + full stats\n396\t- [ ] `GET /public-profile/:identifier` is public (no auth), resolves user_id or username\n397\t- [ ] Public endpoint returns only `gamesPlayed`, `totalWins`, `winRate` — no wallet, no PnL, no wagered, no streaks, no tx history\n398\t- [ ] `avatarUrl` null means use identicon (frontend responsibility)\n399\t- [ ] BigInt fields serialized as strings"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa94e491-d3b8-48ec-9244-f434c72362a9","uuid":"1edc8a25-de10-4010-b53d-f5f71e965f38","timestamp":"2026-03-31T14:03:11.881Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/008-user-profile/spec.md","content":"\n### FR-5: SOL/USD Price Display\n\nTransaction amounts are stored in lamports. The frontend displays them in SOL\nwith a USD estimate using the Pyth SOL/USD price feed (Hermes REST API —\nalready used for Close Call BTC/USD prices).\n\n- Backend exposes a cached `GET /price/sol-usd` endpoint (or piggybacks on an\n  existing price infrastructure). Cache TTL ~60s.\n- Frontend fetches the SOL/USD price and displays amounts as e.g.\n  `0.50 SOL (~$75.00)`.\n- If price is unavailable, show SOL amount only (no USD estimate). No error\n  state — graceful degradation.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [x] Backend serves cached SOL/USD price from Pyth Hermes <!-- satisfied: routes/price.ts:10-66 — HermesClient, SOL/USD feed, 60s TTL cache, stale-on-error -->\n- [x] Frontend displays lamport amounts as SOL with USD estimate <!-- satisfied: ProfileTransactions.tsx:14-24 formatSol(amount, solPrice) → \"0.50 SOL (~$75.00)\" -->\n- [x] Graceful fallback to SOL-only when price unavailable <!-- satisfied: useSolPrice.ts returns null on error; formatSol omits USD when price=null -->\n\n---\n\n### FR-6: Player Profile Record\n\nA `player_profiles` table that stores the player's identity. Created automatically\non first wallet auth (JWT challenge-response) or waitlist signup. The wallet is\nstored internally but **never exposed in API responses** — all public-facing\nreferences use `user_id` or `username`.\n\n**Schema:**\n\n| Column | Type | Constraints | Notes |\n|--------|------|-------------|-------|\n| `id` | `BIGSERIAL` | PK | Internal DB key (not exposed) |\n| `user_id` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Short random string, e.g. `usr_a8f3k2`. Public-facing identifier for API calls |\n| `wallet` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Player wallet address. **Never exposed in public API responses** |\n| `username` | `TEXT` | UNIQUE, NOT NULL | Auto-generated on creation. Editable (freeform, 30-day cooldown) |\n| `username_updated_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | | Null until first manual edit. Cooldown enforced from this timestamp |\n| `avatar_url` | `TEXT` | | Null = use deterministic identicon derived from wallet. Explicit URL for future unlock/upload |\n| `heat_multiplier` | `NUMERIC` | DEFAULT 1.0 | Reserved slot — always 1.0 until HEAT feature ships |\n| `points_balance` | `BIGINT` | DEFAULT 0 | Reserved slot — always 0 until Points feature ships |\n| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | NOT NULL DEFAULT now() | Profile creation time |\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `uq_player_profiles_user_id` on `(user_id)` — public lookup\n- `uq_player_profiles_wallet` on `(wallet)` — internal lookup / auth join\n- `uq_player_profiles_username` on `(username)` — username lookup\n\n**User ID format:** `usr_` prefix + 8 random alphanumeric characters (lowercase).\nGenerated once at profile creation, immutable.\n\n**Username auto-generation:** `{adjective}-{noun}-{4digits}`. On collision, retry\nwith new random suffix (max 5 retries, then fall back to `user-{random8}`).\n\n**Username edit rules:**\n- Freeform: 3-20 characters, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`, no spaces\n- Unique (case-insensitive)\n- Editable once per 30 days (enforced via `username_updated_at`)\n- First manual edit is free (cooldown starts from that edit, not from creation)\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Migration `013_player_profiles.sql` creates table + indexes\n- [ ] Profile auto-created on first JWT auth (challenge-response verify endpoint)\n- [ ] Profile auto-created on waitlist signup (if applicable entry point exists)\n- [ ] `user_id` is a short random string (`usr_` + 8 alphanumeric), immutable after creation\n- [ ] Username auto-generated as `{adjective}-{noun}-{4digits}`, collision-safe\n- [ ] Wallet address never appears in any public API response\n- [ ] `heat_multiplier` and `points_balance` are reserved columns, default values only\n\n### FR-7: Username Management API\n\nPlayers can view and change their username.\n\n**Endpoints:**\n\n`PUT /profile/username`\n- Auth: JWT required\n- Body: `{ \"username\": \"my-new-name\" }`\n- Validates: 3-20 chars, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`, unique (case-insensitive), 30-day cooldown\n- Returns: `{ \"username\": \"my-new-name\", \"nextEditAvailableAt\": \"2026-05-01T...\" }`\n- Errors: 400 (invalid format), 409 (taken), 429 (cooldown not expired)\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Username change validates format (3-20 chars, `[a-zA-Z0-9_-]`)\n- [ ] Username uniqueness enforced case-insensitively\n- [ ] 30-day cooldown enforced from `username_updated_at`; first edit is free\n- [ ] Successful edit updates both `username` and `username_updated_at`\n- [ ] Returns next available edit timestamp in response\n\n### FR-8: Aggregate Player Stats API\n\nComputed stats from the existing `transactions` table. Served as part of the\nprofile response (own profile) or public lookup (limited subset).\n\n**Own profile stats (authenticated):**\n\n| Stat | Computation |\n|------|-------------|\n| `gamesPlayed` | COUNT(DISTINCT match_id) where tx_type = 'deposit' |\n| `totalWagered` | SUM(amount_lamports) where tx_type = 'deposit' |\n| `totalWins` | COUNT(*) where tx_type = 'payout' |\n| `winRate` | totalWins / gamesPlayed (0 if no games) |\n| `winStreakCurrent` | Consecutive most-recent wins (across all games) |\n| `winStreakBest` | Longest-ever consecutive win streak |\n| `netPnl` | SUM(payout + refund) - SUM(deposit) |\n| `gameBreakdown` | Per-game version of above (keyed by game name) |\n\n**Public stats (visible to others via lookup):**\n\n| Stat | Included |\n|------|----------|\n| `gamesPlayed` | Yes |\n| `totalWins` | Yes |\n| `winRate` | Yes |\n| `totalWagered` | **No** |\n| `netPnl` | **No** |\n| `winStreakCurrent` | **No** |\n| `winStreakBest` | **No** |\n| `gameBreakdown` | **No** |\n\n**Win streak logic:** Ordered by `created_at DESC`, across all games. A `payout`\nrow = win. A `deposit` row with no corresponding `payout` for the same `match_id`\n= loss. Refunds don't break or extend streaks. Streak resets on first loss\nwalking backward from most recent game.\n\n**Performance note:** Stats can be computed on-the-fly for now (single query per\nrequest). If latency becomes a problem, add a `player_stats_cache` materialized\nview or summary table later — but don't pre-optimize.\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] `gamesPlayed`, `totalWagered`, `totalWins`, `winRate` computed correctly from `transactions`\n- [ ] `winStreakCurrent` counts consecutive most-recent wins across all games\n- [ ] `winStreakBest` tracks the longest-ever streak\n- [ ] `netPnl` = total inflows (payout + refund) minus total outflows (deposit)\n- [ ] `gameBreakdown` returns per-game stats keyed by frontend game name\n- [ ] Public stats expose only `gamesPlayed`, `totalWins`, `winRate`\n\n### FR-9: Profile API Endpoints\n\nAll profile interaction points for the frontend.\n\n**Endpoints:**\n\n`GET /profile/me` (authenticated)\n- Returns: full own profile + full stats\n- Response shape:\n  ```json\n  {\n    \"userId\": \"usr_a8f3k2\",\n    \"username\": \"fierce-dragon-4821\",\n    \"avatarUrl\": null,\n    \"heatMultiplier\": 1.0,\n    \"pointsBalance\": \"0\",\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"gamesPlayed\": 42,\n      \"totalWagered\": \"150000000000\",\n      \"totalWins\": 23,\n      \"winRate\": 0.5476,\n      \"winStreakCurrent\": 3,\n      \"winStreakBest\": 7,\n      \"netPnl\": \"5000000000\",\n      \"gameBreakdown\": {\n        \"coinflip\": { \"gamesPlayed\": 20, \"totalWins\": 11, \"winRate\": 0.55, \"totalWagered\": \"...\", \"netPnl\": \"...\" },\n        \"lord-of-rngs\": { ... },\n        \"close-call\": { ... }\n      }\n    },\n    \"usernameNextEditAt\": \"2026-05-01T00:00:00Z\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-15T10:00:00Z\"\n  }\n  ```\n- `avatarUrl` null means frontend should render identicon from `userId`\n- `totalWagered`, `netPnl`, `pointsBalance` as strings (BigInt safety)\n\n`GET /public-profile/:identifier` (public, no auth)\n- Mounted at `/public-profile` (separate from `/profile/*` to avoid JWT middleware)\n- `:identifier` resolves to either `user_id` (starts with `usr_`) or `username`\n- Returns: public profile (no wallet, no tx history, limited stats)\n- Response shape:\n  ```json\n  {\n    \"userId\": \"usr_a8f3k2\",\n    \"username\": \"fierce-dragon-4821\",\n    \"avatarUrl\": null,\n    \"heatMultiplier\": 1.0,\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"gamesPlayed\": 42,\n      \"totalWins\": 23,\n      \"winRate\": 0.5476\n    },\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-15T10:00:00Z\"\n  }\n  ```\n- 404 if identifier not found\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] `GET /profile/me` requires JWT, returns full profile + full stats\n- [ ] `GET /public-profile/:identifier` is public (no auth), resolves user_id or username\n- [ ] Public endpoint returns only `gamesPlayed`, `totalWins`, `winRate` — no wallet, no PnL, no wagered, no streaks, no tx history\n- [ ] `avatarUrl` null means use identicon (frontend responsibility)\n- [ ] BigInt fields serialized as strings","numLines":200,"startLine":200,"totalLines":684}}}
