n---------------------+--------------------------+-----------+----------+---------------------------------------------\n id                  | bigint                   |           | not null | nextval('player_profiles_id_seq'::regclass)\n user_id             | text                     |           | not null | \n wallet              | text                     |           | not null | \n username            | text                     |           | not null | \n username_updated_at | timestamp with time zone |           |          | \n avatar_url          | text                     |           |          | \n heat_multiplier     | numeric                  |           | not null | 1.0\n points_balance      | bigint                   |           | not null | 0\n created_at          | timestamp with time zone |           | not null | now()\nIndexes:\n    \"player_profiles_pkey\" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)\n    \"idx_player_profiles_username_lower\" UNIQUE, btree (lower(username))\n    \"player_profiles_user_id_key\" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (user_id)\n    \"player_profiles_username_key\" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (username)\n    \"player_profiles_wallet_key\" UNIQUE CONSTRAINT, btree (wallet)\n\nDATABASE_URL=postgres://vscode@localhost:5432/rng_utopia_dev","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
